BITUTECT, Inc., et al., Appellants, v. The PATENT & LICENSING CORPORATION, Appellee. No. 8529. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 3, 1937.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and HANEY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of appellee, ordered appeal herein dismissed for failure of appellants to file record and docket cause, that a decree of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly, and the mandate of this court issue forthwith.
